      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TARWILLIE (2) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his slick win the start prior, getting around The Meadows over 525m in 30.00. Smart win two back and looks a key chance here. WHO SHE RULES (1) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (24.25) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. ASTON BOREALIS (4) looks close to another win after hitting the frame in a 1.75 lengths third (25.86) in a T3 RSTW at Ballarat. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Winning chance. WHERE'S HUNTLY (3) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a half a length second (24.55) in a T3 RSTW at this track.",
